content.rendered:
Directed by RJ Balaji . N.J. Saravanan

Written by RJ Balaji. N.J. Saravanan

Star RJ Balaji (Ilango). Sathyaraj (Unnikrishnan). Urvashi (Krishnaveni). Aparna Balamurali (Sowmya). K.P.A.C. Lalitha (Unni’s mother). Visvesh (Aniruth). Pavitra Lokesh (Sowmya’s mother). Mayilsamy (Unni’s neighbour). Pugazh (Amal). Deepa Shankar (Deepa). George Maryan (Dr. George). Nakkalites Dhanam (Dhanam). Seema (Unni’s sister-in-law). Ravikumar (Unni’s brother).Rama . Shivani Narayanan (Shalini). Kamala Kamesh (Dr. Jenny). Pradeep Kottayam (Bijulal). Kavithalaya Krishnan (Varadharajan). Sangeetha Venkatesh (Unni’s neighbour). Jagan Krishnan (Unni’s neighbour). Yogi Babu (Coaching center owner)

Language Tamil

Producers Boney Kapoor

Production Bayview Projects. Zee Studios
